    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this dependable ride that\u2019s full of character! While it shows some honest signs of its journey through life, both inside and out, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great price. It's the perfect opportunity to own a capable vehicle that still has plenty of miles left to give!",
